@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_coflky(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v1 + 0.42)) / wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.16)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.34)) / 0.48)
    v2 = (wp.abs(v2) - wp.cos((tmp + 0.78 / v1 + 0.78)))
    v0 = wp.cos((v2 / (tmp + 0.22 * v0 + 0.73)))
    tmp = ((0.91 * wp.exp(v0 + 0.74)) / ((tmp + 0.80 / v0 + 0.93) * wp.cos(v1 + 0.07)))
    v2 = v2
    v0 = ((0.24 + 0.95) * ((v1 + 0.29 / tmp + 0.19) * wp.sin(v2 + 0.06)))
    tmp = v1
    data[tid] = v0
